As lady right suggests the notion of killing Thirst, a figred adorned in 
black robes moves out from the shadows, seemingly melting out from them. A 
large matellic claw is raised and placed upon her hand as two glowing white 
eyes shin from beneath the figures hood.

Void: "His death.. is not neccessary.... he can benefit us another way..."
